&lt;li>&lt;strong>Fast&lt;/strong>: Static sites load instantly&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Cheap&lt;/strong>: Firebase free tier handles tons of traffic&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Simple&lt;/strong>: No databases, no server maintenance&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>SEO-ready&lt;/strong>: Hugo generates clean, optimized HTML&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Here&amp;rsquo;s exactly how I built this site in under 30 minutes.&lt;/p>
