&lt;li>&lt;strong>Firebase Hosting&lt;/strong>: Google&amp;rsquo;s CDN with free SSL&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>AWeber&lt;/strong>: Newsletter forms that actually work&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Google Analytics&lt;/strong>: Track what people read&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
