&lt;p>Look, I&amp;rsquo;ll be honest with you. Last week I caught myself manually checking disk space on 15 servers. FIFTEEN. Like some kind of caveman clicking through Server Manager while my coffee got cold.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>That&amp;rsquo;s when I remembered why I got into this job in the first place - to make computers do the boring stuff so I don&amp;rsquo;t have to. If you&amp;rsquo;re still doing repetitive tasks manually, this post is for you.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>